variable.name: FAMID
variable.description: Unique de-identified ID for family of subject

variable.name: MOTHER
variable.description: Unique, de-identied identification number for mother of subject

variable.name: FATHER
variable.description: Unique, de-identied identification number for father of subject

variable.name: TWINID
variable.description: ID for twins. Twins of the same family should share the same TWINID but be assigned different SUBJIDs.
